<emphasis id="B969EAD48727FFD84218A65961340CFC" bold="true" box="[1052,1073,1663,1687]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">2)</emphasis>
Ventral habitus; 
<emphasis id="B969EAD48727FFD842E4A65961F30CFC" bold="true" box="[1248,1270,1663,1687]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">3)</emphasis>
Lateral habitus; 
<emphasis id="B969EAD48727FFD84693A68565A80CD0" bold="true" box="[151,173,1699,1723]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">4)</emphasis>
