<emphasis id="B969EAD48727FFD84779A68564960CD0" bold="true" box="[381,403,1699,1723]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">5)</emphasis>
Elytral sculpturing.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="8BA236C68727FFD846C3A6C161310D4F" blockId="3.[151,1437,1767,2036]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">
<emphasis id="B969EAD48727FFD846C3A6C164780D6A" bold="true" box="[199,381,1767,1793]" pageId="3" pageNumber="592">
